<bibRefCitation author="Bertolani" box="[453,790,1862,1888]" pageId="21" pageNumber="28" refString="Bertolani, R. &amp; Rebecchi, L. (1993) A revision of Macrobiotus hufelandi group (Tardigrada, Macrobiotidae), with some observations on the taxonomic characthers of eutardigrades. Zoologica Scripta, 22 (2), 127 - 152." type="journal article" year="1993">
